20:28.564 --> 20:32.928
And in those 400 years, we don't have any information about what happened on earth.

20:33.429 --> 20:35.591
We've got no gospel, we've got no testament.

20:36.011 --> 20:38.113
All we have is quiet.

20:40.735 --> 20:44.319
That's 146,000 days of silence.

20:45.460 --> 20:48.202
Six generations came and went.

20:49.103 --> 20:51.986
And the Jews were waiting for their Messiah.

20:52.322 --> 20:56.808
their deliverer to come and free them from the Roman Empire.

20:57.448 --> 21:02.034
I wonder how you or I would respond when we've been promised something, but it hadn't been delivered.

21:02.255 --> 21:04.778
Who knows if you promise you kid something, you've got to deliver.

21:06.059 --> 21:07.701
If not, they nag you till you do.

21:09.584 --> 21:16.172
If you've been made a promise and it's not delivered, we get impatient, we can get frustrated, we can feel let down.

21:16.252 --> 21:20.818
And eventually what happens is we give up, we give up, we lose confidence.

21:21.826 --> 21:27.053
But this is what was said of the Jewish people as they waited for their Messiah.

21:27.213 --> 21:29.777
Remember 400 years of waiting.

21:32.020 --> 21:35.565
And here's what we read in Luke chapter three, verse 15.

21:36.426 --> 21:45.458
It says, the people were in expectation and are all questioning in their hearts concerning John, whether he might be the Christ.

21:45.762 --> 21:50.228
When all the people were baptized, it came to pass that Jesus also was baptized.

21:50.248 --> 21:57.356
And while he prayed, the heaven was opened and the Holy Spirit descended in bodily form like a dove upon him.

21:57.697 --> 22:05.507
And a voice came from heaven which said, you are my beloved son, and you I am well pleased.

22:05.527 --> 22:09.952
The Jewish people waited in expectation.

22:11.174 --> 22:14.578
Could this be the one to deliver them from

22:14.882 --> 22:18.949
occupation of the Romans, economic and political oppression.

22:20.351 --> 22:29.125
But it said this, it said, when the people were in expectation, then the Holy Spirit descended.

22:30.307 --> 22:36.697
I wonder whether expectation attracts the Holy Spirit in our lives.

22:38.440 --> 22:42.066
Are we heading into 2026

22:42.178 --> 22:46.082
with a spirit of trepidation or a spirit of expectation.

22:46.542 --> 22:52.288
Because the Bible is clear here, when there was expectation, the Holy Spirit descended.

22:52.588 --> 22:58.754
Who knows we need a fresh touch of the Holy Spirit to descend on our city and our nation at this time?

22:59.394 --> 23:08.023
