23:21.700 --> 23:22.822
Great expectations.

23:24.163 --> 23:25.465
Great expectations.

23:26.587 --> 23:34.418
My prayer is that the Holy Spirit would release great expectations over you for this new year.

23:34.882 --> 23:40.953
