23:57.188 --> 24:01.412
It changes when the people lift their expectations.

24:01.712 --> 24:05.575
When they have great expectations for what God is going to do.

24:05.835 --> 24:15.644
I don't just want to go through the routine, the rhythm of another year, another service, another well-being Wednesday, another chapel service, another staff meeting.

24:15.804 --> 24:21.809
We've got to have a greater expectation that God can do something supernatural in our lives.

24:21.989 --> 24:24.932
When the people are in expectation, the holy

24:24.912 --> 24:26.094
spirit to send it.

24:28.097 --> 24:29.679
We've got to lift our expectation.

24:31.782 --> 24:33.264
Maybe our city can be saved.

24:37.350 --> 24:37.830
Say that again.

24:37.911 --> 24:39.653
Maybe our city can be saved.

24:40.414 --> 24:50.168
The picture I have in my head of dancing outside City Hall, the whole street in front of City Hall with laughter and joy and dancing in the streets.

24:50.408 --> 24:51.570
I've got this thing

24:51.682 --> 24:52.783
I can't shake it.

24:52.803 --> 24:57.808
I don't know how it's going to happen or when it's going to happen, but I've got an expectation that choose joy.

24:57.828 --> 25:00.290
It wasn't just a word for the soul church.

25:00.611 --> 25:02.092
It was a word for this season.

25:02.292 --> 25:04.354
The joy is going to return to the streets.

25:04.594 --> 25:08.678
The Spirit of the Lord God is going to fall again on this city.

25:08.879 --> 25:11.161
There will be one more great Reformation.

25:11.441 --> 25:16.766
There will be one more great revival, but it starts when we change our expectation.

25:19.008 --> 25:20.690
It starts with expectation.

25:21.442 --> 25:23.646
So the question is, what are you expecting this year?

25:26.791 --> 25:27.933
What do you expectations?

25:29.295 --> 25:35.746
