25:52.054 --> 25:54.297
God can transform the University of East Anglia.

25:54.557 --> 25:56.219
God can transform the art college.

25:56.480 --> 25:58.502
God can transform the city college.

25:58.522 --> 25:59.964
God can move in the schools.

26:00.224 --> 26:01.065
God can move.

26:01.246 --> 26:08.895
There can be an outpouring at the Holy Spirit like we have never seen in this city, but it starts with the spirit of expectation.

26:13.141 --> 26:13.821
