26:40.166 --> 26:43.229
You don't come to church at 11 p.m. unless you're expecting God to move.

26:44.711 --> 26:45.071
You don't.

26:45.712 --> 26:47.474
You just stay in bed or stay watching a movie.

26:48.322 --> 26:54.111
