27:04.907 --> 27:07.931
They arrived with a sense of God, I'm ready to cross over.

27:08.192 --> 27:09.614
I'm ready to go into a new year.

27:09.854 --> 27:14.962
I'm ready to lift up my, you know, we've got to treat every Sunday like it's Resurrection Sunday.

27:16.450 --> 27:20.434
It's amazing on Easter Sunday, you guys come expecting.

27:22.596 --> 27:29.663
We've got to come to church expecting, we're expecting salvation, supernatural healings.

27:29.683 --> 27:33.647
We've got to expect people to find God in a new and real way this year.

27:34.768 --> 27:35.609
Expectation.

27:36.270 --> 27:38.452
Teen challenge, I just want you to know we love you boys.

27:38.973 --> 27:44.338
