27:45.698 --> 27:49.765
My expectation is you're going to break free from some of those things that have held you back.

27:50.125 --> 27:52.770
My expectation is you're going to be reunited with family.

27:53.010 --> 27:57.257
My expectation is God's going to use your story mightily for the kingdom of God.

27:57.418 --> 28:00.883
You've got to lift your expectation for what God can do.

