28:10.279 --> 28:12.082
Wonder what your expectation is for this year.

28:12.738 --> 28:17.767
Wonder if you read the headlines and you've put your expectation down into the ground.

28:18.508 --> 28:19.650
Lift your eyes to the hills.

28:21.072 --> 28:22.395
Come on, lift your eyes to the hills.

28:22.435 --> 28:23.617
That's where your help comes from.

28:23.877 --> 28:25.079
The business is going to sell.

28:25.360 --> 28:26.943
There's going to be a breakthrough coming.

28:27.103 --> 28:38.162
There's contracts arriving, but we've got to change our expectation for the new year is when we change our expectation, the Holy Spirit begins to hover and move over those businesses.

28:40.578 --> 28:49.406
You know, the opposite to expectation is unbelief, but the very essence of unbelief in the faith is expectations.

28:51.609 --> 28:59.696
I believe in today as we pray, you know, we could have not stopped the last service because the Spirit of God was moving so powerfully.

29:00.377 --> 29:07.364
