29:49.937 --> 29:52.460
We've got to expect blessing over our families.

29:54.602 --> 29:57.285
So what have you accepted and stopped expecting in your life?

29:59.607 --> 30:00.548
We're not here to settle.

30:02.250 --> 30:03.771
