30:03.791 --> 30:10.418
So I want to just share really quickly the next four and a half hours, three ways to live with a spirit of expectation.

30:12.226 --> 30:16.613
three ways to live the spirit of great expectations.

30:16.693 --> 30:19.437
Number one is this, you've got to pray in expectation.

30:21.020 --> 30:28.612
It says in verse 21, when all the people were baptized, it came to pass that Jesus was also baptized while he prayed the heavens were opened.

30:29.393 --> 30:34.521
The first thing Jesus did, after his baptism, he prayed in expectation.

30:35.062 --> 30:37.707
Look what happened when he prayed, the heavens opened.

30:39.049 --> 30:39.890
The heavens opened.

30:41.250 --> 30:43.112
Could the heavens open again over the city?

30:47.055 --> 30:47.736
We're going to pray.

30:48.637 --> 30:59.067
We're going to pray one more time before our Lord returns that the heavens will open again over this nation, over this nation, over Europe.

30:59.727 --> 31:05.393
We watch Chantal and I and the family watch the Bonhoeffer movie on Amazon Prime last night.

31:05.453 --> 31:09.196
