31:21.785 --> 31:23.208
I've got to stand for my faith.

31:24.330 --> 31:25.432
I've got to stand for truth.

31:25.833 --> 31:27.276
We've got to stand for righteousness.

31:27.677 --> 31:30.002
But Bonhoeffer, he was a man who loved to pray.

31:30.370 --> 31:31.553
and he would seek God.

31:31.994 --> 31:40.011
And the Nazis heard him praying and they were getting touched and filled with the Spirit of God outside his prison cell as he sought God and he heard him.

31:40.031 --> 31:45.123
And he was leading Nazis to the Lord in his prison cell simply because he prayed.

31:45.343 --> 31:47.207
Because when you pray, here's what happens.

31:47.468 --> 31:48.370
The heavens open.

31:49.378 --> 31:53.403
and anybody under that open heaven will get a touch of the presence of God.

31:53.663 --> 31:58.729
I would encourage you as you seek God and as you pray, the heavens will open over your business.

31:58.949 --> 32:00.891
