32:56.760 --> 32:58.222
Chantal and I, we will not allow it.

32:58.422 --> 33:01.126
We're going to stay focused on the cause of Jesus.

33:01.406 --> 33:02.227
He's my rock.

33:02.547 --> 33:03.569
He's my fortress.

33:05.371 --> 33:08.355
The people were an expectation.

33:09.096 --> 33:09.556
The people.

33:10.798 --> 33:12.380
The people.

33:12.400 --> 33:14.162
Be careful who you hang out with this year.

33:15.362 --> 33:21.731
If you've got a negative cynical, conspiring spirit, a jaded spirit, ask the Holy Spirit to help you.

