40:01.174 --> 40:03.497
The power of the Holy Spirit, He wants to unite you.

40:04.478 --> 40:08.784
Don't allow anything to stand between you and your future.

40:12.029 --> 40:15.474
And then we've got to listen and expectation.

40:16.642 --> 40:21.688
Just pause and listen to the Holy Spirit.

40:21.708 --> 40:22.569
Thank you, Jesus.

40:25.232 --> 40:30.278
Thank you all.

40:31.079 --> 40:33.082
Be still and know that He is God.

40:39.269 --> 40:39.890
Jesus.

40:47.650 --> 40:48.991
He gives strength to the weary.

40:50.813 --> 40:52.515
