41:13.956 --> 41:16.498
When you pass through the rivers, they will not sweep over you.

41:17.474 --> 41:20.499
You will walk through the fire and you will not be burned.

41:21.381 --> 41:23.765
The flames will not set you ablaze.

41:24.726 --> 41:27.071
Says the Lord.

41:27.091 --> 41:27.551
Amen.

41:28.934 --> 41:29.996
Amen.

41:30.016 --> 41:32.660
I've written a declaration for this year.

41:32.700 --> 41:43.058
It'll go up on the line so you can take a copy, but I wanted you to declare this out because what I've just spoken, I've put this into a declaration and I want you to use this

41:43.266 --> 41:46.670
as a way just to speak faith over your future, over your 2026.

41:47.050 --> 41:47.751
Is that okay?

41:48.572 --> 41:49.473
Okay, I'm going to read a line.

41:49.493 --> 41:50.614
I want you to repeat it after me.

41:51.155 --> 41:51.515
You ready?

41:52.416 --> 41:56.461
In 2026, I walk as a child of God.

41:56.481 --> 42:03.568
I boldly confess the Word of God over every area of my life.

42:05.290 --> 42:12.338
I live under an open heaven and I expect God's favor, protection,

42:12.962 --> 42:17.309
and blessings over my family and my loved ones.

42:18.190 --> 42:33.593
My family, my home, and my possessions are divinely protected from every accident, incident, injury, disease, illness, and financial loss.

42:34.815 --> 42:41.906
I expect circumstances to align in my favor because I am a child of God

42:43.106 --> 42:48.373
I expect to be healthy, physically fit and strong.

42:49.194 --> 42:51.577
I will age, but not decay.

42:52.538 --> 43:01.029
My strength is renewed and my body responds to the life of God within me.

43:01.770 --> 43:04.493
I am the head and not the tail.

43:05.334 --> 43:07.897
I am above only and not beneath.

43:08.678 --> 43:11.602
I am the lender and not the borrower.

43:12.322 --> 43:26.598
I wait in confident expectation for your Holy Spirit to release miracles, breakthroughs and divine opportunities over my life.

43:27.679 --> 43:38.150
I choose the spirit of expectation this week, this year and every day of 2026.

43:39.552 --> 43:41.394
Amen.

43:41.506 --> 43:49.598
Right now, maybe a friend invited you to church.

43:49.959 --> 43:51.822
Maybe you've come back off the back of the wonder.

43:52.943 --> 44:02.818
Maybe you're just checking it out because you see the way the world is going and you heard that there's some light on Hartsey's Lane and you were attracted to it.

44:03.800 --> 44:06.023
A friend, however you've got here today is irrelevant.

44:06.043 --> 44:08.587
The fact is you're here and God loves you.

44:09.448 --> 44:10.610
God's got a plan for you.

44:11.778 --> 44:18.084
God sent his one and only son Jesus to this earth as a baby as we've just remembered at Christmas, but he lived.

44:18.645 --> 44:20.166
He died a cruel death on a cross.

44:20.667 --> 44:21.487
He was crucified.

44:22.148 --> 44:23.770
But three days later, he rose again.

44:23.790 --> 44:27.573
And on that cross, he took your sin, your shame, your guilt.

44:28.314 --> 44:30.016
He took everything you've ever done.

44:30.056 --> 44:34.039
And he said, I take that pain.

44:34.059 --> 44:38.003
I take that sin for you because he loves you.

44:39.465 --> 44:40.946
God's got a plan for your life.

44:41.826 --> 44:44.269
Maybe you've never heard this for a long time, but he loves you.

44:45.410 --> 44:45.951
He loves you.

44:46.832 --> 44:51.837
But you've got to make a decision to receive that love, because that love is a gift.

44:52.838 --> 44:55.221
And gifts have to be received as well as given.

44:55.241 --> 44:58.084
Well, that gift is freely given today.

44:58.725 --> 45:00.667
The question is, will it be freely received?

45:02.048 --> 45:05.532
Maybe you once walked with God, but you've walked away.

45:05.572 --> 45:08.856
Life's taken you down a different path.

45:09.437 --> 45:10.738
Well, today you can come back.

45:11.458 --> 45:14.222
And you too can live with great expectations for your future.

45:16.586 --> 45:17.668
It starts with a decision.

45:19.831 --> 45:23.957
January the 4th, 2026 can be a life transforming day in your life.

45:24.819 --> 45:30.327
It can be a day that you'll remember forever if you make that decision today to receive his love and receive his grace.

45:30.768 --> 45:32.991
Friend, God's got a plan for your future.

45:33.733 --> 45:35.836
All you have to do is receive that gift today.

45:36.577 --> 45:39.762
So I'm going to count to three from the floor on the tiered seats,

45:39.938 --> 45:45.265
Those watching online, you say John today, I wanna receive that gift of forgiveness, of life, of purpose.

45:45.625 --> 45:49.530
All I want you to do is just slip up your hand, say John, would you pray for me?

45:50.130 --> 45:52.253
Every Christian praying with expectation right now.

45:52.593 --> 45:54.235
Let's believe for people to find Christ.

45:54.516 --> 45:56.719
I'm gonna count to three, one, two, three.

45:56.859 --> 45:58.300
Just slip up your hand and say pray for me.

45:58.581 --> 46:00.383
God bless you, God bless you, God bless you.

46:00.824 --> 46:02.165
Beautiful, lift it up nice and high.

46:04.588 --> 46:05.169
God bless you.

46:08.833 --> 46:09.394
God bless you.

46:10.274 --> 46:11.656
All right, you can put your hands down.

46:11.716 --> 46:12.257
God bless you.

46:12.978 --> 46:15.061
We're going to say this prayer out loud together.

46:15.602 --> 46:21.712
Dear Lord Jesus, thank you for dying for me to forgive all my sins and failures.

46:23.575 --> 46:28.182
I believe that you rose from the dead so that I can have a brand new life.

46:29.283 --> 46:36.995
Please come into my heart and help me by the power of the Holy Spirit to trust and to live for you.

46:38.257 --> 46:38.738
Amen.

46:39.202 --> 46:39.663
Amen.

46:39.723 --> 46:43.389
Can we congratulate everyone who's prayed that salvation prayer?

46:46.814 --> 46:48.277
We want to give you a gift.

46:48.337 --> 46:52.864
If you prayed that prayer, or maybe you didn't lift up your hand, the hand really bit is irrelevant.

46:52.884 --> 46:54.186
It's just so I know who I'm praying for.

46:54.627 --> 46:55.548
This is Gemma down here.

46:55.568 --> 46:56.390
It gives a wave, Gemma.

46:56.910 --> 46:59.154
And we want to give you a gift at the end of the service.

46:59.266 --> 47:01.732
As soon as we conclude, just head over to this little chapel area.

47:01.752 --> 47:02.573
We want to give you a gift.

47:02.614 --> 47:03.195
It's the Bible.

47:03.596 --> 47:05.420
And we want to help you as you take your next step.

47:05.620 --> 47:08.827
But that's the greatest decision that you can ever make with your life.

47:09.208 --> 47:12.716
And you can now live with great expectations for your days ahead.

47:12.756 --> 47:13.257
Amen.

47:13.839 --> 47:15.643
Fantastic.

47:15.663 --> 47:17.106
Thanks again for tuning in.

47:17.282 --> 47:25.112
If you said yes to Jesus today by saying the Salvation Prayer, we'd love for you to email connections at soulchurch.com.

47:25.412 --> 47:29.978
So we can talk to you a little bit more about this incredible decision you've just made.

47:30.619 --> 47:39.069
And if at any point in the service, you felt moved to give towards any of our local or global initiatives, head to soulchurch.com.

47:39.089 --> 47:46.098
And don't forget to stay connected with us on Facebook, Instagram, and YouTube by searching at Soul Church UK.

47:46.402 --> 47:47.954
Take care and God bless.

